  "keyFeatures": [
    "Motor and differential motor group abstractions",
    "Advanced chassis control with odometry and PID",
    "Motion profiling with asymmetric trapezoidal profiles",
    "Multiple autonomous movement algorithms (boomerang, move-to-point, pose control)",
    "Controller wrapper with customizable drive curves and input handling",
    "Piston control with toggle functionality",
    "Comprehensive utility functions for angles, geometry, and timing",
    "Exit condition system for autonomous routines"
